dmca.title: User-Submitted Photos in a Ranking List Alleged to Violate Copyright
dmca.body:
Gentlemen,

THIS  MATTER  REQUIRES  YOUR  IMMEDIATE  ATTENTION.

This Notice of Claimed Infringement is sent to you the Internet Service Provider pursuant to section 512(c) of the United States Copyright Act of 1976 (as amended), 17 U.S.C.
